entry.title: shitiven/GitPower
entry.summary:
A fast, secure and stable solution based on Python & Django

GitPower Demo

Installation Guide

Requirements

  • Python >= 2.5 && Python <= 2.7
  • The django support database (defalut mysql)
  • Redis server
  • pip tool
  • sshd-vcs

Install python requirements

sudo pip install -r requirements.txt
